Goldman Sachs Trust II - Multi-Manager International Equity Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 8:15 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Goldman Sachs Trust II - Multi-Manager International Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Goldman Sachs Trust II - Multi-Manager International Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Goldman Sachs Asset Management, L.P. The fund is co-managed by Causeway Capital Management LLC, Massachusetts Financial Services Company, and WCM Investment Management. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe excluding the United States. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors such as business stability, succession planning, team development, pas...
Goldman Sachs Trust II - Multi-Manager International Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Goldman Sachs Asset Management, L.P. The fund is co-managed by Causeway Capital Management LLC, Massachusetts Financial Services Company, and WCM Investment Management. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe excluding the United States. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors such as business stability, succession planning, team development, past and expected investment performance, ability to navigate in varying market conditions, risk management techniques, and liquidity of investments to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI EAFE Index (Net, USD, Unhedged). Goldman Sachs Trust II - Multi-Manager International Equity Fund was formed on July 31, 2015 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


200 West StreetNew York, NY 10282United StatesFounded in 2015



Phone: 212-902-1000

Fax: 212-357-5281

assetmanagement.gs.com/content/gsam/us/en/individual/products/fund-finder.html#activeTab=factsTab&fi







